{"tid":187081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺業主/地主係社會上最低賤既階層","createTime":"2017-04-04T16:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T16:31:38.000Z","uid":80788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8298ab969b7ebd8037642161af7cfb1a4c5656","tid":187081,"uid":80788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"尤其是講緊無正職/承繼上一代物業架人<br />\n收入就只係靠分人地profit/人工維持生活<br />\n如果叫佢地去做生意/打工，可能佢地又未必搵得到咁多<br />\n到人地搵得多，又靠加租去食人地一大截<br />\n根本係對社會零貢獻既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇左佢地個社會運作仲暢順左<br />\n諗起都覺得低賤"},{"pid":"4908ffeb32e57d9347ae45c3efbd5a0e8a8e5f52","tid":187081,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"不事生產，淨喺將自己獨占嘅資源租比人賺錢<br />\n大家生於世上應該人人平等，可以共同分享世上自然資源，好似空氣同陽光咁每人都可以免費使用，但唯獨是&ldquo;土地&rdquo;比班仆街霸佔咗先，結果後人想用&ldquo;土地&rdquo;就要比錢佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd04599fdb6f8b2a0fe26f2023ebb5c697e043ad","tid":187081,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"不過一個唔小心就變左共產主義"},{"pid":"8adbcb791f1211766c94f4d17b20ed80e565852f","tid":187081,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"做唔到先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ec528a5f0077109d9726a0457afab28be780db","tid":187081,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/184295/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/184295/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fae762acbcaa797606a45ece6c396057b0e59364","tid":187081,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"支持共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f02e2831e5072095fd941b4d29a74eba78ad8","tid":187081,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl